{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she believed this person and went back to the apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, we weren't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you can imagine what a tremendous reunion it was when my grandmother brought us in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- so that was, needless to say, if it wasn't for my grandma at that point, there wouldn't be any-- You wouldn't have been there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wouldn't be any interview right now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was, of course, the real bad, bad beginning of-- and of course, when we got to the apartment, everything was gone in the apartment, everything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One thing my mother did, her father told her that to hide all the jewelry, and gold, and diamonds in a bucket.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he made a bucket for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A bucket that you have a false bottom on it, OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, in Europe, everybody always had a bucket of water next to the fireplace.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was this bucket with a false bottom sitting next to the fireplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, everything was taken from the apartment, but the bucket was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the bottom of the bucket, which had all this gold and diamonds was intact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Which, as I-- as we go through the story, you'll see how important later on those things did help.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was kind of the bad beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At this point--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at this point, they started-- they-- there was a ghetto set aside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact-- you know, and I looked up some data on this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, this isn't what I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Stanislawow, the Jewish council in Stanislawow worked out-- and the Germans worked out an area of a ghetto area where the Jews would be.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think everyone knows what a ghetto is.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
